&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ANINE BING&lt;/strong&gt; is looking for an &lt;strong&gt;ADV Manager EU&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Wholesale team, based at our Paris HQ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is an opportunity to help shape the next chapter of ANINE BING. As the first dedicated Sales Administration leader for our European wholesale business, the ADV Manager EU owns the operational backbone of our EU growth — from order management and Key Account compliance to customer service and warehouse coordination. You will free our commercial leadership to focus on account development, and you will build the infrastructure required to reclaim markets currently operated under agent contracts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who thrives in a creative yet performance-driven environment — sharp on detail, clear on the big picture, collaborative, and energized by building something that does not yet exist at the brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hybrid position based at our Paris HQ, with a preference for in-person work. The role reports to the EU Wholesale Manager with a functional dotted line to our Global Operations team in Los Angeles.&lt;/p&gt;
