&lt;li&gt;Ensuring 100% shipping compliance for our top Key Accounts (Zalando, Beymen, Harrods, Galeries Lafayette, and others) — managing portals and seasonal catalogs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as the primary EU point of contact for our 3PL warehouse partner (Bleckmann, Belgium) and for our network of EU sales agents and in-house Key Accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Producing weekly delivery reports and stocklists for agents and Key Accounts, and handling all follow-up on swaps, reorders, RMAs, and claims.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and maintaining operational KPI dashboards (OTIF, chargebacks, book-to-ship) to inform commercial decisions and Key Account business reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the expansion and optimization of sales back-office systems to accommodate the future internalization of territories currently operated under regional agent contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnering cross-functionally with Global Operations (NY), Finance, and the Paris Wholesale team to ensure consistency, compliance, and scalability across the EU.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
