&lt;li&gt;Fluent English and French; a third European language (German, Italian, or Spanish) is a strong plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable experience with an ERP system (NetSuite preferred), 3PL warehouse coordination, and Key Account portals such as Zalando, Farfetch, Net-a-Porter or Harrods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of the commercial mechanics of wholesale fashion — market calendars, agent networks, Key Account dynamics, and compliance frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
