&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1–2 years of relevant design experience, including internships or freelance work; experience with fashion or lifestyle brands is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong portfolio demonstrating graphic design work across e-commerce, marketing, and digital channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Adobe Creative Suite (Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign); familiarity with Figma or motion design is a bonus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meticulous attention to detail with a strong sense of composition, balance, and visual consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and collaboration skills; receptive to feedback and eager to grow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep interest in fashion, branding, and visual storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated with a proactive, hands-on mindset and ability to work independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
