&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work/Life Balance:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Enjoy flexible work schedules, generous paid time off, and additional summer days to recharge and reset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wellness:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We offer comprehensive medical, dental, and vision coverage—with ANINE BING covering a significant portion of the cost. Our benefits extend to your family and include a generous parental leave program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Style Perks:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Enjoy a generous employee discount and seasonal wardrobe allotments—so you can live the brand, not just represent it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
